---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout pageTitle="Hire">
  <div class="text-content">
    <div>
      <h1>Hire Me</h1>
      <p>
        I am actively seeking new opportunities in education and technology. My primary focus is on the following roles:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <b>Adjunct Faculty:</b> Entry-level IT jobs, Windows and Linux administration, and entry-level programming (Remote
          or in-person in the New Port Richey, FL area).
        </li>
        <li><b>Instructional Design:</b> Part-time, remote opportunities.</li>
        <li><b>Web Development:</b> Bringing your ideas to life through modern web solutions.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>I am a lifelong learner, dedicated to both expanding my own knowledge and helping others grow theirs.</p>

      <p>Please feel free to get in touch if you have a project you think I'd be a good fit for.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div
        class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 font-mono text-sm relative group hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors flex flex-col h-full !mt-0">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 border-b border-zinc-800 pb-2">
          <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div>
          <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div>
          <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/50"></div>
          <span class="ml-2 text-xs text-zinc-100">review_01.txt</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-zinc-200 mb-4 flex-grow">
          <span class="text-emerald-500">$</span> cat review_01.txt<br /><br />
          "You have been a vital part of our department. Can 't wait to see what 2026 has to offer!"
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs text-zinc-100 border-t border-zinc-800 pt-3 flex flex-col items-end gap-1 mt-auto w-full">
          <span class="font-semibold">-- John Stewart</span>
          <span class="text-zinc-400 text-right">Program Director, Polk State College</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div
        class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 font-mono text-sm relative group hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors flex flex-col h-full !mt-0">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 border-b border-zinc-800 pb-2">
          <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div>
          <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div>
          <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/50"></div>
          <span class="ml-2 text-xs text-zinc-100">review_02.txt</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-zinc-200 mb-4 flex-grow">
          <span class="text-emerald-500">$</span> cat review_02.txt<br />
          "I can't recommend Solomon enough. He's a baller, shot caller."
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs text-zinc-100 border-t border-zinc-800 pt-3 flex flex-col items-end gap-1 mt-auto w-full">
          <span class="font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">-- Joseph Smith</span>
          <span class="text-zinc-400 text-right">Some Dude</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div
        class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-4 font-mono text-sm relative group hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors flex flex-col h-full !mt-0">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 border-b border-zinc-800 pb-2">
          <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div>
          <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div>
          <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/50"></div>
          <span class="ml-2 text-xs text-zinc-100">review_03.txt</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-zinc-200 mb-4 flex-grow">
          <span class="text-emerald-500">$</span> cat review_03.txt<br />
          "He's a mean one, Mr. Grinch."
        </div>
        <div class="text-xs text-zinc-100 border-t border-zinc-800 pt-3 flex flex-col items-end gap-1 mt-auto w-full">
          <span class="font-semibold">-- Every Who</span>
          <span class="text-zinc-400 text-right">Whoville</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
